David and Sandra Greatrex from Plymouth were harassed by David's sister Anne Duffy . 
  Anne had set up her brother with one of her best friends . 
  She was jealous of the relationship and sent Sandra threatening text messages . 
  She then cancelled her brother's wedding using a fake email address . 
  David and Sandra took Anne to court and she was jailed for eight weeks . 
  Family Secrets and Lies airs on Channel 5 tonight . 
 